\c 20
\s UJehoshafathi unqoba amaMowabi lamaAmoni
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi emva kwalokho abantwana bakoMowabi\x + 2 Kho. 1.1. 2 Kho. 3.4, 7.\x* labantwana bakoAmoni\x + 1 Sam. 11.1.\x* bela\add banye\add* ngaphandle kwamaAmoni beza bamelana loJehoshafathi empini\x + 26.7. 20.10,22,23. Hlu. 10.12. 1 Lan. 4.41.\x*.
\v 2 Kwasekusiza \add abanye\add* babikela uJehoshafathi besithi: Kuyeza ixuku elikhulu ukumelana lawe elivela phetsheya kolwandle, eSiriya; khangela-ke, liseHazazoni-Tamari\x + Gen. 14.7.\x*, eyiEngedi\x + 1 Sam. 23.29.\x*.
\v 3 UJehoshafathi wasesesaba, wamisa ubuso bakhe ukudinga iN\nd kosi\x + 19.3. 1 Lan. 22.19.\x*\nd*, wamemezela ukuzila ukudla kuye wonke uJuda\x + Ezra 8.21. Jer. 36.9. Jona 3.5. Jow. 1.14. 2.15.\x*.
\v 4 UJuda wasezibuthanisa ukudinga eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; lasemizini yonke yakoJuda baphuma beza ukudinga iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 5 UJehoshafathi wasesima ebandleni lakoJuda leJerusalema endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd* phambi kweguma elitsha.
\v 6 Wasesithi: N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu wabobaba, wena kawusuye yini uNkulunkulu emazulwini\x + Dute. 4.39. 1 Kho. 8.23.\x*? Yebo, \add ka\add*wubus\add i\add* yini kuyo yonke imibuso yezizwe? Lesandleni sakho kukhona amandla lengalo, ukuze kungabi khona ongamelana lawe\x + 1 Lan. 29.12. Dan. 4.17,25,32. Mat. 6.13.\x*.
\v 7 KawusiNkulunkulu wethu yini\x + Gen. 17.7. Eks. 6.7.\x*? Uxotshile abahlali balelilizwe elifeni phambi kwabantu bakho uIsrayeli, walinika inzalo kaAbrahama\x + Hlab. 44.2. Eks. 15.9.\x* umngane wakho kuze kube phakade\x + Isa. 41.8. Jak. 2.23.\x*.
\v 8 Basebehlala kilo, bakwakhela indawo engcwele kulo eyebizo lakho, besithi:
\v 9 Uba kusehlela phezu kwethu ububi, inkemba, isahlulelo, loba umatshayabhuqe wesifo, loba indlala\x + 6.28-30. 1 Kho. 8.33,37.\x*, sizakuma phambi kwalindlu laphambi kwakho\x + Ezra 10.1.\x* (ngoba ibizo lakho likulindlu\x + 6.20.\x*), sikhale kuwe ekubandezelekeni kwethu, uzakuzwa-ke usindise.
\v 10 Ngakho-ke, khangela, abantwana bakoAmoni labakoMowabi\x + 20.1,22,23.\x* labentabeni iSeyiri\x + 25.11,14. Gen. 36.8. Gen. 32.3.\x* ongavumanga ukuthi uIsrayeli adlule phakathi kwabo lapho besuka elizweni leGibhithe\x + Dute. 2.4,9,19.\x*, kodwa babafulathela kabababhubhisanga\x + Nani 20.21.\x*;
\v 11 khangela-ke, basivuza beza uku\add za\add*sixotsha elifeni lakho owenze ukuthi silidle\x + Hlab. 83.6,7,12.\x*.
\v 12 Nkulunkulu wethu, kawuyikubahlulela yini\x + 1 Sam. 3.13.\x*? Ngoba amandla kawakho kithi okumelana lalelixuku elikhulu elize ukumelana lathi; njalo thina kasikwazi esingakwenza, kodwa amehlo ethu akuwe\x + Hlab. 25.15. 123.1,2. 141.8.\x*.
\v 13 UJuda wonke wasesima phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, lensane zabo, omkabo labantwana babo.
\p
\v 14 Khona uJahaziyeli indodana kaZekhariya indodana kaBhenaya indodana kaJeyiyeli indodana kaMathaniya, umLevi emadodaneni kaAsafi\x + Hlab. 83.1.\x*, uMoya weN\nd kosi\nd* wafika phezu kwakhe phakathi kwebandla\x + Nani 24.2. Hlu. 3.10.\x*.
\v 15 Wasesithi: Lalelani lonke bakoJuda labahlali beJerusalema, lawe nkosi Jehoshafathi; itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* kini: Lina lingesabi lingatshaywa luvalo ngenxa yalelixuku elikhulu\x + 20.17. 32.7. Dute. 1.29,30. 31.6,8.\x*, ngoba impi kayisiyo yenu, kodwa ngekaNkulunkulu\x + 1 Sam. 17.47.\x*.
\v 16 Kusasa yehlani limelane labo; khangela, bayenyuka ngomqanso weZizi; lizabathola ekucineni kwesihotsha phambi kwenkangala yeJeruweli.
\v 17 Kakusikwenu ukulwa kule \add impi\add*; zimiseni lime, libone usindiso lweN\nd kosi\nd* lani\x + Eks. 14.13,14. Hlu. 7.21.\x*, Juda leJerusalema. Lingesabi lingatshaywa luvalo\x + 20.17. 32.7. Dute. 1.29,30. 31.6,8.\x*; kusasa phumani limelene labo, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* izakuba lani\x + 15.2. 32.8. Nani 14.9. Roma 8.31.\x*.
\v 18 UJehoshafathi wasekhothamisa ikhanda emhlabathini, laye wonke uJuda labahlali beJerusalema bawa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, beyikhonza iN\nd kosi\x + 29.29,30. Neh. 8.6. Eks. 4.31.\x*\nd*.
\v 19 AmaLevi kubantwana bakoKohathi\x + Eks. 6.16,18.\x* lakubantwana bakoKora asesukuma ukudumisa iN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 6.24. Nani 26.58. 1 Lan. 9.19,31. 26.1,19.\x*\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, ngelizwi elikhulu eliphezulu.
\p
\v 20 Basebevuka ekuseni kakhulu, baphuma baya enkangala yeThekhowa\x + 2 Sam. 14.2.\x*; lekuphumeni kwabo uJehoshafathi wema wathi: Ngilalelani Juda labahlali beJerusalema. Kholwani eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wenu, lizaqiniswa; likholwe kubaprofethi bayo, lizaphumelela\x + Isa. 7.9.\x*.
\v 21 Esecebisene labantu wamisela iN\nd kosi\nd* abahlabeleli, abazadumisa ubuhle bobungcwele\x + 1 Lan. 16.29.\x*, ekuphumeni phambi kwabahlomileyo, besithi: Dumisani iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba umusa wayo \add umi\add* kuze kube nininini\x + 1 Lan. 16.34,41.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Kwathi lapho beqalisa ukuhlabelela lokudumisa, iN\nd kosi\nd* yabeka abacathameli\x + 13.13.\x* ukumelana labantwana bakoAmoni\x + 20.10.\x*, uMowabi, lentaba iSeyiri, ababezemelana loJuda; basebetshaywa.
\v 23 Ngoba abantwana bakoAmoni labakoMowabi basukuma bamelana labahlali bentaba yeSeyiri ukutshabalalisa lokuchitha\x + 13.13.\x*; njalo sebebaqedile abahlali beSeyiri, bancedisa ngulowo umakhelwane wakhe encithakalweni\x + Hlu. 7.22. 1 Sam. 14.20.\x*.
\v 24 UJuda esefikile enqabeni yokulinda enkangala bakhangela ngasexukwini, khangela-ke, kwakulezidumbu eziwele emhlabathini; njalo kungekho ophephileyo.
\v 25 UJehoshafathi labantu bakhe sebefikile ukuphanga impango bathola phakathi kwabo ngobunengi, impahla lazo, lezidumbu, lezinto eziligugu, baziphangela baze \add b\add*ehluleka uku\add zi\add*thwala. Njalo baba lensuku ezintathu bephanga impango ngoba yayinengi\x + 32.27. 36.10. Gen. 27.15.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Njalo ngosuku lwesine babuthana esihotsheni seBeraka, ngoba lapho bayibusisa iN\nd kosi\nd*; ngenxa yalokho babiza ibizo laleyondawo \add ngokuthi\add* yisihotsha seBeraka kuze kube lamuhla.
\v 27 Basebebuyela, wonke umuntu wakoJuda leJerusalema, loJehoshafathi enhlokweni yabo, ukuthi babuyele eJerusalema belentokozo, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yabathokozisa phezu kwezitha zabo\x + Neh. 12.43.\x*.
\v 28 Basebengena eJerusalema belezigubhu zezintambo lamachacho lezimpondo, baya endlini yeN\nd kosi\x + 1 Lan. 15.16.\x*\nd*.
\v 29 Uvalo ngoNkulunkulu lwaselusiba phezu kwayo yonke imibuso yamazwe lapho besizwa ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* yalwa lezitha zikaIsrayeli\x + 14.14. 17.10.\x*.
\v 30 Ngakho umbuso kaJehoshafathi waba lokuthula, ngoba uNkulunkulu wakhe wamphumuza inhlangothi zonke\x + 14.14. 17.10.\x*.
\s Ukubusa kukaJehoshafathi
\p
\v 31 UJehoshafathi wabusa-ke phezu kukaJuda; wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu lanhlanu lapho esiba yinkosi, wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amabili lanhlanu eJerusalema. Lebizo likanina lalinguAzuba indodakazi kaShilehi.
\v 32 Wasehamba ngendlela kayise uAsa, kaphambukanga kuyo, esenza okulungileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\x + 1 Kho. 22.41-43.\x*\nd*.
\v 33 Lanxa kunjalo indawo eziphakemeyo kazisuswanga\x + 17.6.\x*; ngoba abantu babelokhu bengalungisanga inhliziyo yabo kuNkulunkulu waboyise\x + 12.14. 19.3.\x*.
\p
\v 34 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaJehoshafathi, ezokuqala lezokucina, khangela, zibhaliwe ezindabeni zikaJehu indodana kaHanani\x + 1 Lan. 29.29.\x* ezagoqelwa egwalweni lwamakhosi akoIsrayeli\x + 1 Kho. 16.1. 1 Kho. 22.45.\x*.
\p
\v 35 Lemva kwalokho uJehoshafathi inkosi yakoJuda wazihlanganisa loAhaziya inkosi yakoIsrayeli owenza ngenkohlakalo ekwenzeni\x + 1 Kho. 22.48-50.\x*.
\v 36 Wasezihlanganisa laye ukwenza imikhumbi yokuya eTarshishi; basebeyenza imikhumbi eEziyoni-Geberi.
\v 37 UEliyezeri indodana kaDodavahu weMaresha waseprofetha emelene loJehoshafathi\x + 11.8.\x* esithi: Ngoba uzihlanganise loAhaziya, iN\nd kosi\nd* yephulile imisebenzi yakho\x + 19.2.\x*. Ngakho imikhumbi yephuka, ayaze yenelisa ukuya eTarshishi\x + 1 Lan. 29.14.\x*.
